        <mxCell id="ekr3Sa7Gujgn25rdjJ_G-186" value="The submarine can hold a small quantity of purified water.&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;In areas where the water is extremely toxic, water may become scarce and slow to filter.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
