        <mxCell id="ekr3Sa7Gujgn25rdjJ_G-193" value="The prison can hold Norbert&#39;s follower so they can be interrogated later.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;The prison can also hold any other crew members that are causing trouble.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
